286
00:16:12,670 --> 00:16:14,030
Just stay put.

287
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:23,600
Lord Wang.

288
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:26,320
There's no one named Shan in this area.

289
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:29,270
Try searching further west.

290
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:30,600
Many thanks, sir.

291
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,630
I shall take my leave.

292
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:37,200
Are you Mr. Wang Heng?

293
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:38,720
You're looking for me?

294
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:40,990
Someone named Shan

295
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,150
wishes to meet you.

296
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:44,000
But he can't show himself.

297
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,330
Here's the address.

298
00:16:54,940 --> 00:16:56,860
(Tavern at the East Market in the city)

299
00:17:14,820 --> 00:17:17,220
♪Watch the storm;
