312
00:17:51,780 --> 00:17:56,820
♪To live so as to shake the world♪

313
00:17:57,180 --> 00:18:01,300
♪With this journey,
I gain a fiercer edge♪

314
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:03,500
♪I've planned
before I act countless times♪

315
00:18:03,580 --> 00:18:09,940
♪Fatal danger turned into a jest♪

316
00:18:10,060 --> 00:18:14,260
♪Through this road,
I watch the endless rise and fall♪

317
00:18:14,300 --> 00:18:16,380
♪In the chapters lie ages
of decay and bloom♪

318
00:18:16,380 --> 00:18:18,300
♪Let us meet again♪

319
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:23,500
